Sentencas: A fluidized coal bed-solid oxide fuel cell (FB-SOFC) arrangement is employed for efficient conversion of dry gasified coal into electricity at 850 degrees C.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: It consists of an anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell of 24 cm(2) active area coupled to a Boudouard gasifier.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: A minimally fluidized bed Of low Sulfur (0.15 wt%) Alaska coal is gasified at 930 degrees C by flowing CO(2) to generate CO.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: The resulting CO fuel is oxidized at the Ni/YSZ cermet anode.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: The highest cell power density achieved is 0.45 W cm(-2) at 0.64 V with 35.7% electrical conversion efficiency based on CO utilization.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: This power density is the highest reported in the literature for such systems and corresponds to a total power generation of 10.8 W by this cell.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal

Sentencas: Similarly, 48.4% is the highest conversion efficiency measured at a power density of 0.30 W cm(-2) and 0.7 V. The open circuit voltages are in good agreement with values expected based on thermodynamic data.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cell operating on dry gasified coal
